Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.55,0:33:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.16,0:33:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.56,0:33:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(难道说要做爱吗？)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.13,0:34:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.17,0:34:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好大的
